---
title: Chicken & Bacon Parmigiana with Spiced Fries, Double Cheese & Garlic Aioli
description: Who doesn’t love a good parmigiana? Take it to new levels by adding rashers of bacon for a protein combo that sure is easy to
love. Paired with crispy fries and aioli, we bet it'll feel like a gourmet pub-bistro night tonight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-bacon-parmigiana-9f818694.jpg
